Package DataCollection

Class MapData

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataCollection.MapData

  • public class MapData
extends java.lang.Object
    Map Data class takes a file and parses it based on white space then calculates air temperature min, max, and average at 1.5 meters and 9 meters as well as solar radiation min, max, and average. This is then printed out.
    Version:
    2018-12-05
    Author:
    Tim Weaver
